Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.49,0:01:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好难画喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.47,0:01:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道挑简单一点的画就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.64,0:01:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.08,0:01:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.61,0:02:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.49,0:02:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑞尔，你连画画都很行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.22,0:02:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.47,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…对你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.91,0:02:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.35,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有人在看这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有谁在看你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.38,0:03:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被看的人是你啦，小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也真是辛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.43,0:03:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好不容易鼓起勇气\N想向小樱表白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.20,0:03:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果被小可破坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次你要什么时候跟她说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还不想告诉她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.38,0:03:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我只想着\N一定要告诉她才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.42,0:03:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有些事我得先处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.19,0:03:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第60话 小樱与她重要的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她约好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.43,0:04:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我有喜欢的人之前\N要当莓铃的未婚夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.37,0:04:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要把现在的心情告诉莓铃，是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.88,0:04:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天晚上打电话给她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说有事要当面告诉她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.38,0:04:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃怎么说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她问我不能在电话里告诉她吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.99,0:04:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉她想当面告诉她\N她说她知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.46,0:04:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好跟莓铃谈过\N然后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再告诉她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候要去见莓铃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.87,0:04:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放寒假我要回香港\N到时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等不了那么久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.25,0:04:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打电话之后\N她就马上来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.16,0:04:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃怎么可能等到放寒假…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么突然来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.87,0:05:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来办点事\N对不对？小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.15,0:05:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要在这里待多久？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.19,0:05:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要上学\N所以明天就得赶回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那今天呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.46,0:05:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后\N我们一起去玩好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.70,0:05:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过，不过\N你是来办事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以可能没空吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.14,0:05:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子，木之本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那放学后在校门口见啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾，我今天要去学游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.76,0:06:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去学钢琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.43,0:06:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要替我们多陪莓铃聊聊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.30,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去跟寺田老师打声招呼\N待会见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，我马上就回来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.26,0:06:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊？我现在打得正过瘾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然这时候打来，真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可，你又在打电动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.41,0:06:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是小樱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一下我就要破四亿分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要跟莓铃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.25,0:07:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会晚点回去\N要记得打开电锅的开关喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个臭丫头来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过她说明天就要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我今天想跟她聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉那个臭丫头一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.29,0:07:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我要让她看到我超酷的样子\N叫她别吓得腿软了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.77,0:07:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了电锅喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.76,0:07:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起\N我打扰你打电话了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有，我刚刚讲完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.73,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才班上来了一位\N我没见过的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.84,0:07:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,头发长长的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.20,0:07:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫作李莓铃\N是我们以前的同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.44,0:08:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一学期结束时\N她回香港去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐的就是她的位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是小狼的表妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.98,0:08:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.65,0:08:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们约好今天放学后一起去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.69,0:08:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天色暗了会比较危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.53,0:08:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么笑嘻嘻的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.71,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为能见到你，我很高兴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.78,0:08:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这点小事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是小事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.25,0:08:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以见到你\N我真的非常非常高兴嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.22,0:08:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，能再见到你我也很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:09:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，那么最后\N你成为库洛牌的新主人啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是怪事仍继续再发生，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吗？\N因为木之本总是呆呆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.31,0:09:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么是呆呆的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.68,0:09:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呆呆的就是呆呆的啊\N这不需要解释吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来好像很轻的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.25,0:09:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么解释才好呢\N日文应该是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要今天告诉莓铃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然我的心意已决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不说的话\N就等于是对莓铃毁约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.27,0:09:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要遵守我跟莓铃的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很像你的作风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.04,0:09:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你是这样的人\N莓铃才会喜欢上你的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说\N又开了一间新的果汁店喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.02,0:09:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里的综合果汁好好喝喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们到那里聊聊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有库洛先生的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有股强大魔力的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.63,0:10:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.49,0:11:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世，小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你刚才说的怪事，是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.54,0:11:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.38,0:11:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷帝召来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.76,0:11:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷帝召来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.57,0:11:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃，小樱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.55,0:12:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有办法对付那个啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有那么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.69,0:12:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下怎么打得完嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.77,0:12:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶\N要是能让他们不动的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.17,0:12:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若用树牌，无法一次捉住它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.74,0:13:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若用时牌，以我的魔力来说\N也不知道可以暂停多久时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.15,0:13:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天气这么冷，怎么会发生这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.42,0:13:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用那个啦，那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在溜冰场捉到的那张牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将大家冰冻起来的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冻牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕴藏星星力量的钥匙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显现真正的神力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.67,0:13:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据契约，小樱命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除封印！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛创造的库洛牌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.28,0:13:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃旧有姿态\N重新转生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.35,0:13:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以新主人，小樱之名命令你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.02,0:13:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“冻”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.81,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷帝召来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.29,0:14:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这都多亏莓铃想到这个好方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.26,0:14:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃，小樱\N有没有受伤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是莓铃帮了我的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知世你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.11,0:14:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.38,0:14:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，莓铃你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃，你受伤了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.48,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事，我很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.90,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是靠香港女孩的建议\N而让他们得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果不能去喝果汁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.09,0:16:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么刚才都没人经过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明闹成那个样子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是移动企鹅的人搞的鬼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.80,0:16:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想起来\N以前发生怪事的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.93,0:16:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近也都没人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.34,0:16:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事做得到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是魔力很强的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.31,0:16:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔力很强的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜欢你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么突然这么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.29,0:16:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事\N请你都要想起我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃\N你明天搭几点的飞机？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上10点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.68,0:17:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊，我们要上学\N不能去送你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后再见面不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本跟香港就像在隔壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.86,0:17:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以见面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.55,0:17:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有了最喜欢的人\N我们约好了要告诉你，对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.69,0:17:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经有了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.33,0:17:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.17,0:18:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…木之本吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.48,0:18:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.78,0:18:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是叫她小樱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.78,0:18:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会叫女生的名字\N除了你姊姊之外就只有我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.46,0:18:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们取消婚约吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去大道寺家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天没跟她说到话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经很晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.88,0:18:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，我送你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.53,0:18:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的，我搭计程车去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.23,0:18:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我会从大道寺家直接去机场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让她静一静吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.43,0:19:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.50,0:19:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是…\N我是全世界最喜欢小狼的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.84,0:19:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝不会输给任何人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.28,0:19:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更让我生气的事是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.99,0:19:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样\N我还是不会讨厌木之本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.96,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜欢木之本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.33,0:20:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.80,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼会喜欢上木之本\N这也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.80,0:20:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我是这么想的\N可是我哭又是另外一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我要哭到眼睛融化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.98,0:20:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要哭到死\N哭到不会再为小狼而哭为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.33,0:20:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛肿肿的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.20,0:20:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会，你跟平常一样可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.94,0:20:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，你站在那里干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来送我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.26,0:21:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉木之本了吗？\N说你喜欢她了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.07,0:21:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没吗？真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.44,0:21:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木之本那种人\N你不说她是不会知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.24,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不选这么可爱的我\N而选了木之本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.08,0:21:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们不好好相处\N我绝不原谅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.05,0:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.12,0:21:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放假的时候要回来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.29,0:21:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.60,0:21:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃小姐真是心地善良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃寄信来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.78,0:22:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也收到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.25,0:22:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她给你的信上写些什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.09,0:22:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说“对不起弄湿了你的膝盖”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.03,0:22:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你的信上写什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.36,0:22:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说我呆呆的\N所以要我多看清楚一点四周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.40,0:22:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她说我有很多事都没注意到\N所以她很担心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.51,0:22:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有最后的这个，你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.78,0:22:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么念，是什么意思\N我虽然不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.72,0:22:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信一定是一句好话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.43,0:22:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得好高兴喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.61,0:23:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝迟钝的小狼\N赶快表白得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.54,0:23:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在香港的天空下为你祈祷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.25,0:23:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓铃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.22,0:23:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最重要的朋友，李小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.20,0:24:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节就要到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.97,0:24:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟哥哥约好\N要一起去买圣诞礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.74,0:24:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有库洛先生的气息？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.71,0:24:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕，我得快点赶去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.24,0:24:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是可是\N我跟哥哥约好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.28,0:24:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库洛魔法使\N“小樱、库洛牌与礼物”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.45,0:24:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也与小樱一起\N解除封印！
